Bronze for Brazil | Beijing 2008 | Sports | The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata)
                                                                                                                                                                                                             Bronze for Brazil
                      
	Shanghai: Brazil overcame their deep frustration at not making the mens Olympic football final by putting away Belgium 3-0 to take the bronze medal at the Shanghai Stadium on Friday.         
	Goals from Diego and Jo in the first half and a second by Jo just before the final whistle settled the outcome. Ronaldinho motivated the team with a masterful display. (PTI)                                                                                                                          
